data.description: Well maintained and updated three bedroom two bath home situated on a corner lot.  Recent updates include new flooring throughout, all new front and back porch and freshly painted inside and out.  Roof was recently replaced in 2017 and there are newer appliances, water heater and AC.  Master bedroom has a nice walk in closet as well as a private bath.  Both guest bedrooms are spacious with roomy closets and share a full guest bath.  The electrical panel has been updated and there is an RV plug as well.  Quite peaceful setting that is also convenient to shopping and restaurants.  Schedule your private showing today!
